                    <p>Hello to anyone reading this passage. My name is Katina and this is my first year @ CRF.   I am so excited to see what amazing blessings God has in store for each of us this year.  I am married with two beautiful girls, Shelby 10, and Jena 4.  I love to play volleyball, and  I am a huge sports nut!  About 6 years ago God put a passion in my heart to work with the youth of our church.  To this day that passion burns larger and brighter than ever, only now he has given me more of you to love.  I look forward to meeting each and every face who knocks on the door of God’s kingdom.</p>
